MockBot Features:

Modules:
========
Audio Soundplay
Openni (kinect)
Arduino (2 servos and 6 analog input ports)
SLAM

http://robotwebtools.org/
MJpegserver and RosBridge
RMS (not finished)

Hardware:
=========
see SPEC directory

Changes:
Current ATOM CPU is too slow for SLAM and more.
I've changed to Intel NUC i3 CPU, 8GB memory and 64GB SSD
It's amazing !!!

